Text-Names version 0.01
=======================

A Perl extension for name parsing and normalization. See POD for details.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Text::Capitalize

